Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.52,0:01:49.20,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}with your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.26,0:01:52.91,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I can hear my heart bell
