Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:58.60,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}天使が鳴らしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.02,0:02:01.41,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}「大好き」の合図だよね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:04.26,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Can you hear my heart bell?
