Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守形学长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.60,0:03:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点突然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能收留我们一阵子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可保证不了你们的生命安全哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.24,0:03:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险  智树
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时期
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近经常会有熊出没
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当心点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  要是留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.41,0:03:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会小命不保的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.09,0:03:33.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小智绝对会到处找内衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不会让你住在我家的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是来我家吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌熊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆被吃掉算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太无情啦  楚原
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看在我们是青梅竹马的份上  这种时候就帮我一把嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你能保证不到我的房间里偷内衣吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.43,0:03:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很愉快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:03:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樱井君要来我们家吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会长会好好款待你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会长家好像是那全镇最大的宅邸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  超名流的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.72,0:04:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的话  见月同学和守形君也一起来如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超名流生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就说定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就此告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在客气什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不像你啊  守形学长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名流  名流
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老夫是美香子的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.51,0:04:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这五月田根家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里还是驿站的江户时代起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.79,0:05:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是掌握着空美镇的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就说  那个「名流」是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:07.88,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,60)}{\fad(900,0)}{\c&H2226d4&\3c&Hffffff&\fs26}任侠道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:07.88,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,35}{\fad(900,0)}{\c&H2226d4&\3c&Hffffff&\fs22}名流
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家也不必这么害怕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不做什么很过分的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请饶我们一命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.73,0:05:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快招呼客人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爷  请用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爷  这也请用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们叫学长少爷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是因为学长和会长是青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关系很好的缘故吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要拉拉看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.89,0:06:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.27,0:06:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  小智他刚刚去洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗澡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这五月田根家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个被称为  「狱门汤」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只允许本族人使用的浴场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿智树这小子别搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:06:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:07:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？想一起泡吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会长我倒是不介意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然敢擅自闯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.54,0:07:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱井君还意外地有胆色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  很可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是赶快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然会被杀掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标正向3点钟方向逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本族神圣的狱门汤中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闯入了一个毛贼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要没命了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯父  救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.43,0:08:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是美香子的友人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,规矩就是规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小智
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狱门汤原本是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月田根家的祖先天女大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗净羽衣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在天女大人离去之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这浴场曾一度向客人开放
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却遭来了天谴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:33.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地震  饥荒  龙卷风
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传闻灾难只有割下客人的头颅才得以平息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.88,0:08:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我族用「狱门汤」这个名称祭拜它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是为了保护空美镇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是美香子的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就尽量给你安乐死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:08:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小智
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美香子  快阻止他们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月田根家的规矩是绝对的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也无法阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  英君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若你们还要继续的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守形的少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你难道想与五月田根家为敌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一边去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.92,0:09:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想对主人做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在问你  你想对我的主人做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手  Ikaros
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惊扰各位了  很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  今天就看在这位小姐的份上饶了你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.59,0:10:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来她不是泛泛之辈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  Ikaros
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.58,0:10:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别太在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.14,0:10:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美香子  善后就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多快到了  大家快起来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.76,0:11:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到无人岛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.85,0:11:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是搞什么啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大海好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是归五月田根一族所有的小岛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:11:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以请各位尽情放松吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  为什么我们会来到无人岛呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是因为某人把重要的规矩破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:09.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果没法继续留在家里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.55,0:12:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是赶各位出去的话又太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想换作去我们家的小岛住就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道给各位添麻烦了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…不  没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了小智居然能做到这个地步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小智  你可要好好谢谢人家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙…招待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得的机会  真想下海游泳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.14,0:12:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别小看无人岛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了生存
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先要确保食物充足
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.16,0:12:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？但是  这是会长家的小岛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该有别墅吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况就是这样  我们没时间玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.97,0:12:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先让Ikaros和智树去负责准备食物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去找能喝的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  Ikaros
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  就在这附近的海里随便抓点鲷鱼或者金枪鱼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机会难得  你就大显身手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现椰子蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错  是椰子蟹耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就想尝一尝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饶了我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊  差一点就被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃动物  找点植物好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.78,0:13:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  肚子饿扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:13:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…很显然是有问题的蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐  别这样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷  爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…失去意识了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.07,0:14:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楚原！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楚原
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.94,0:14:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点  你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  小智你没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.90,0:15:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了  楚原？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没和学长他们在一起吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道  我们在逃跑的途中走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是被这声音追着  拼命逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好怕啊  小智
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  暂时躲一躲  看看情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点  楚原
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  等天亮了  我们去找大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一夜过后  黎明到来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们前去寻找学长和Ikaros他们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  却完全找不到他们  就这样过了数日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了晚上  一定会听到那个声音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小智  难道说学长他们已经被吃掉了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  学长他们怎么会那么简单就被干掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在会长肯定在用无线电求救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓了好多呢  小智
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要加油才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.60,0:16:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  拜托你了  楚原
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样  过了一个月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们两个完全适应了这座岛的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楚原也恢复了笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种生活也不错…什么的  我开始这么想的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？楚原
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:17:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉呢  我只是想起了学长他们的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  小智  我们将来会怎样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是这样永远都没人来救我们的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时就在这里愉快地生活下去就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我在  你不是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让楚原寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小智…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  要是有孩子的话  肯定会更热闹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  有…孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那个…意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:18:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楚…楚原…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.88,0:18:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小…小智…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑  楚原
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:26.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楚原
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.75,0:18:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快动啊  我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  快动起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小智  没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.54,0:18:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开楚原！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开  快放开楚原
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开  快放开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快放开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金枪鱼群实在很难找
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我去了南半球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小智  这个是海带还有牡蛎什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？难道说这些只不过是缠在Ikaros身上的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  在海底行走的时候  被很多东西给缠住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.89,0:20:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说  那个声音是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长他们呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人  要用生命反应雷达探测一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.78,0:20:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀  真是让人看了场好戏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.99,0:20:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是破坏我们一族规矩的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下就可以扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让楚原寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.25,0:20:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小智…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻人真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛  没有送命就不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说我又因为小智而被牵连了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…冷静点  楚原
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.52,0:21:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底都是小智的错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小智大傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.05,0:21:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,房子居然复原了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.86,0:21:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人  那边…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ikaros大姐  你好！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.61,0:21:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.05,0:21:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是五月田根一族的绵薄之礼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.93,0:21:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请务必收下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.37,0:21:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于五月田根来说  力量就是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.55,0:21:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸似乎很看好Ikaros
